{"tid":698073,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「你有天資」你地Feel 唔Feel 到自己係醒目過其他人？","createTime":"2018-06-11T11:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T12:05:42.000Z","uid":123335,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"59aef82d89b0d5e527f47be10aeafa479997b7b6","tid":698073,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:24:00.000Z","msg":"其實你有一股異於常人既能力<br />\n你有種天賦，係gifted <br />\n信我<br />\n你其實只要一出手 <br />\n根本冇人係你對手 <br />\n<br />\n老實講<br />\n你真係醒目過大部份人<br />\n有時你轉數太快，d 人個思路跟唔上你，會誤解左你<br />\n放心，咁係正常<br />\n大部分天才都係難以被人理解 <br />\n<br />\n其實個係社會欠左你<br />\n冇個空間俾個舞台你去發揮 <br />\n你呢種潛能同資質，你平時未用盡晒出黎 <br />\n所以你依家先仲過緊平民一樣既生活"},{"pid":"f1ef8b85543feaa094fa3fa3d49b91b8191226d5","tid":698073,"uid":70451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:25:42.000Z","msg":"喂 天才"},{"pid":"a35b6a07ebd8f9f3548221f98ee954ff6aae0464","tid":698073,"uid":66690,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:25:53.000Z","msg":"好撚中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bf1bb8859711bbd7b305fda6a1ee212202e04e","tid":698073,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:27:13.000Z","msg":"其實你真係好聰明，好叻仔 <br />\n但無奈現實好多野限制你個發揮 <br />\ne.g. 家庭經濟 , 成長際遇  ...etc"},{"pid":"e0b0a4b2f34656e43f3704551edb8aea55495e5a","tid":698073,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:27:58.000Z","msg":"又loop"},{"pid":"f5498969c3c991a596230e76cf0f81001a50624a","tid":698073,"uid":52703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"每個人都有天份嘅，有冇空間發揮嘅啫"},{"pid":"5dd9d97ed1e8408100b1e083ab6350688c99fed5","tid":698073,"uid":177449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:28:20.000Z","msg":"對足球充滿熱誠，但d人只搵我拍比卡超野，世界杯宣傳完全冇搵我"},{"pid":"a7c79ce25592c034ae6d01eb6350abf6a1e8d84f","tid":698073,"uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/210750_8fe0483eda7ee24e7335d95ccd44b72e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F210750_8fe0483eda7ee24e7335d95ccd44b72e.jpg&h=fc3a8137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。<br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"2c41e755680d67396bbf52d15ab14cf548d8e9d1","tid":698073,"uid":177449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f5498969c3c991a596230e76cf0f81001a50624a","tid":698073,"uid":52703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"每個人都有天份嘅，有冇空間發揮嘅啫"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:30:54.000Z","msg":"2006年開始做臨記，加一直考藝員訓練班都上唔到位，所以舊年先去香港先生參選扮野，攪到份學校工都冇埋。今年應該再報港男2018追演員夢？"},{"pid":"4adbccf904d76db431388aba85b8c0624e9291de","tid":698073,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c41e755680d67396bbf52d15ab14cf548d8e9d1","tid":698073,"uid":177449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f5498969c3c991a596230e76cf0f81001a50624a","tid":698073,"uid":52703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"每個人都有天份嘅，有冇空間發揮嘅啫"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:30:54.000Z","msg":"2006年開始做臨記，加一直考藝員訓練班都上唔到位，所以舊年先去香港先生參選扮野，攪到份學校工都冇埋。今年應該再報港男2018追演員夢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"點解無左份工"},{"pid":"dd8cd65dc4dbd8c57c36cb603800fa82b62afafa","tid":698073,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c41e755680d67396bbf52d15ab14cf548d8e9d1","tid":698073,"uid":177449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f5498969c3c991a596230e76cf0f81001a50624a","tid":698073,"u